        <cell>\Lower{Negation}</cell>
        <cell>\Lower{<m>\left( {\exists x \in \mathbb{Z}} \right)\left( {\forall y \in \mathbb{Z}} \right)\left( {x + y \ne 0} \right)</m>}</cell>
        <cell>There exists an integer  <m>x</m>  such that for every integer  <m>y</m>,  <m>x + y \ne 0</m>.</cell>
